be leaving in five minutes.

21
00:01:20,122 --> 00:01:22,499
[Paula] Jesus.
Look at all these numties.

22
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:25,293
Every single one of them
on a device.

23
00:01:25,294 --> 00:01:28,046
Glued to a screen, giving
all their data away for free.

24
00:01:28,047 --> 00:01:30,632
- [ringtone playing]
- Not a single book
between them.

25
00:01:30,633 --> 00:01:32,842
Sad what we've become.

26
00:01:32,843 --> 00:01:34,469
Hey, Mum.

27
00:01:34,470 --> 00:01:36,054
Yeah, we're just leaving Galway.

28
00:01:36,055 --> 00:01:38,515
So will you pick me up in,
like, two hours?

29
00:01:38,516 --> 00:01:40,725
Mum, I've got, like,
half my flat with me,

30
00:01:40,726 --> 00:01:42,560
