Come pick me up.

32
00:01:44,188 --> 00:01:46,189
Aren't you excited
to have your girl

33
00:01:46,190 --> 00:01:48,234
coming home for a few days?

34
00:01:49,443 --> 00:01:51,027
Mum?

35
00:01:51,028 --> 00:01:52,612
Mu...

36
