♪ Loudly laughing
and sharing a joke ♪

235
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:35,176
♪ There's nothing
about each other ♪

236
00:10:35,177 --> 00:10:36,678
♪ That they don't know ♪

237
00:10:38,805 --> 00:10:40,765
- [fingers snap rhythmically]
- ♪ They're so good-looking ♪

238
00:10:40,766 --> 00:10:43,476
♪ And they're both young, too ♪

239
00:10:43,477 --> 00:10:46,563
♪ Looks like
we've got ourselves ♪

240
00:10:48,899 --> 00:10:51,525
♪ A meet cute ♪

241
00:10:51,526 --> 00:10:53,028
♪ It's impossibly cute ♪

242
00:10:54,071 --> 00:10:56,322
♪ Aren't you up for them? ♪

243
00:10:56,323 --> 00:11:00,076
♪ Don't you wish
you were them? ♪

244
00:11:00,077 --> 00:11:01,786
♪ A meet cute ♪

245
00:11:01,787 --> 00:11:03,622
- [meows]
- ♪ It's disgustingly cute ♪

246
00:11:04,915 --> 00:11:07,416
♪ Let's hope that nothing gets
