248
00:11:11,004 --> 00:11:13,422
♪ Yeah ♪

249
00:11:13,423 --> 00:11:16,050
♪ They're just strangers
on a train ♪

250
00:11:16,051 --> 00:11:18,762
♪ Life leads them along ♪

251
00:11:20,097 --> 00:11:21,807
♪ Yeah ♪

252
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:26,685
♪ They're just strangers ♪

253
